---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <h1>Marko Petrov</h1>

    <p>
      I'm a Computer Science student at <a href="https://www.finki.ukim.mk/en">FCSE Skopje</a>,
      focused on deep learning and algorithms. Right now I'm building
      <a href="https://github.com/petrovmarko/MarkGrad">MarkGrad</a>, an autograd engine from
      scratch, and competing in
      <a href="https://www.kaggle.com/competitions/birdclef-2026/overview">BirdCLEF+ 2026</a>.
    </p>

    <p>
      Previously I've worked on competitive programming, statistics, and small ML projects.
      I'm interested in research, startups, and financial markets — and I solve a lot of puzzles.
    </p>

    <p>
      Reach me on
      <a href="https://github.com/petrovmarko">GitHub</a>,
      <a href="https://mk.linkedin.com/in/marko-petrov-926637332">LinkedIn</a>,
      or at <a href="mailto:marko@example.com">marko@example.com</a>.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
</style>
